data.description: This 3/2 concrete block beauty has been completely remodeled and ready for you to move right in.  The roof, A/C, plumbing, electrical and water heater are only 3 years old. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, large eat-in kitchen with quartz countertops, white shaker cabinets and stainless-steel appliances.  Primary Bedroom has a gigantic ensuite bathroom, nice size closet and a walk-in shower with barn doors. There is a large inside laundry room and washer and dryer will stay. Seller just added a nice sized screened in porch a little over a year ago overlooking the large fenced in backyard that backs up to a conservation preserve so there is no one behind you. There is plenty of room to bring your boat or an RV, if you have one. Seller will welcome VA and FHA buyers.
